{
  "stem": "7238.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then he heard that there was a DP camp, a displaced person camp, in Zeilsheim, not far from Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he and his friend came over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in between they worked for the American soldiers in a PX, because he wanted to work and to earn money.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He came to the camp, and there he found me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, in this camp, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was already quite a while, because I gave up looking for more family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not about my sister.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to kill time and to do something positive, as a teacher I collected all the youngsters who survived and gave them a chance to complete their education.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I opened up a high school for grownups.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some were 18, some were 16, some were 20, but they wanted to learn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were other survivors, teachers too, and we had a little school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We gave them-- they needed education that the Germans ordered to be able to go to college.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they got their diplomas, thanks to our help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there one day, he came in, and he found me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was the only one that he remembered from our Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he used to come again, and visiting and working in the PX.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was until we were befriended, and it was until June 12, 1946 we got married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we remained in Zeilsheim in this displaced person camp, until it came the news that everybody has to go to his destination.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They worked to bring us to Israel, at this time Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because in between being in the displaced person camp, I got news that my-- no, this was right after.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got news that my sister survived, with her husband and with her child.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
